OL,3,CFresh wave of asylum hotel protests
OL,4,Cexpected after Epping ruling
OL,6,FA wave of protests outside hotels used
OL,7,Fas temporary accommodation for asylum
OL,8,Fseekers is expected in the coming days.
OL,10,FIt comes as the latest figures showed
OL,11,Fthere were more than 32,000 asylum
OL,12,Fseekers in hotels, marking a rise of
OL,13,F8% during Labour's first year in
OL,14,Foffice.
OL,16,FStand Up To Racism is preparing to
OL,17,Fhold counter-protests outside hotels
OL,18,Fhousing asylum seekers on Friday,
OL,19,Fincluding in Bournemouth, Cardiff and
OL,20,FLeeds, with further demonstrations
OL,21,Fexpected on Saturday.
