OL,3,CFresh wave of asylum hotel protests
OL,4,Cexpected after Epping ruling
OL,6,FMeanwhile, councils across the country
OL,7,Fcontrolled by Labour, the
OL,8,FConservatives and Reform UK are
OL,9,Finvestigating whether they could
OL,10,Fpursue legal challenges against asylum
OL,11,Fhotels.
OL,13,FThis follows a judge granting Epping
OL,14,FForest District Council a temporary
OL,15,Finjunction on Tuesday that blocked
OL,16,Fasylum seekers from being housed at
OL,17,Fthe Bell Hotel in Essex.
