OL,6,FThe council had argued the injunction
OL,7,Fwas needed amid "unprecedented levels
OL,8,Fof protest and disruption" in
OL,9,Fconnection with asylum seeker
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FShadow justice secretary Robert
OL,13,FJenrick said the people of Epping who
OL,14,Fprotested and its council have "led
OL,15,Fthe way", writing in The Telegraph
OL,16,Fthat "our country's patience has
OL,17,Fsnapped".
