OL,6,FHis Conservative colleague Chris
OL,7,FPhilp, the shadow home secretary, said
OL,8,Fon Thursday that people have "every
OL,9,Fright" to protest over asylum hotels
OL,10,Fin their areas.
OL,12,FLabour has pledged to end the use of
OL,13,Fhotels to house asylum seekers by the
OL,14,Fend of this parliament in 2029.
