OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper insisted
OL,7,FLabour had taken "crucial steps" in
OL,8,Fthe past year towards this by cutting
OL,9,Fthe asylum backlog and money spent on
OL,10,Fthe asylum system, increasing returns
OL,11,Fof failed asylum seekers and
OL,12,Foverhauling appeals.
OL,14,FWhile the number of asylum seekers
OL,15,Fhoused in hotels has risen, Government
OL,16,Fspending on asylum in the UK is down
OL,17,F12%, data published on Thursday showed.
