OL,3,CFresh wave of asylum hotel protests
OL,4,Cexpected after Epping ruling
OL,6,FThe number waiting on an initial
OL,7,Fdecision on an asylum application in
OL,8,Fthe UK at the end of June dropped
OL,9,Fbelow 100,000 for the first time in
OL,10,Ffour years.
OL,12,FAsylum seekers and their families can
OL,13,Fbe housed in temporary accommodation,
OL,14,Fknown as contingency accommodation, if
OL,15,Fthey are awaiting assessment of their
OL,16,Fclaim or have had a claim approved and
OL,17,Fthere is not enough longer-term
OL,18,Faccommodation available.
