OL,3,CFresh wave of asylum hotel protests
OL,4,Cexpected after Epping ruling
OL,6,FWhen there is not enough housing, the
OL,7,FHome Office ` which has a legal
OL,8,Fobligation to provide accommodation to
OL,9,Fasylum seekers who would otherwise be
OL,10,Fdestitute ` can move people to
OL,11,Falternatives such as hotels and large
OL,12,Fsites, like former military bases.
OL,14,FAmid hotel protests, campaigners
OL,15,Fincluding Rape Crisis and Refuge have
OL,16,Fwarned conversations about violence
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls are being
OL,18,F"hijacked by an anti-migrant agenda"
OL,19,Fwhich they argued fuels divisions and
OL,20,Fharms survivors.
